<div class="thumbinner" style="width:172px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Usdaeinkorn1_Triticum_monococcum.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/99/Usdaeinkorn1_Triticum_monococcum.jpg/170px-Usdaeinkorn1_Triticum_monococcum.jpg" width="170" height="170" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/99/Usdaeinkorn1_Triticum_monococcum.jpg/255px-Usdaeinkorn1_Triticum_monococcum.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/99/Usdaeinkorn1_Triticum_monococcum.jpg/340px-Usdaeinkorn1_Triticum_monococcum.jpg 2x" data-file-width="1500" data-file-height="1500" /></a>
